{"tid":1526644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8.31後，係咪真係做乜都唔割？","createTime":"2019-09-01T06:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T09:12:41.000Z","uid":2719,"like":218,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3c42f1655474410b24570c27f5e66ccb62c1cb","tid":1526644,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"如果...<br />\n<br />\n1. 接放學發生意外<br />\n(他只是個孩子受傷，和會唔會道德上身)<br />\n<br />\n2. 無差別錫狗<br />\n(和會否指責同狗黑無分別，傷及無辜)<br />\n<br />\n3. 塞交通令你地被罷工<br />\n(指責阻人返工，要求做其他不合作運動)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上三點，我都幾肯定做完又俾人屌。唔係想分化，係太了解和理非前後兩個人。之前塞鐵勁多post話係垃圾不合作運動，會影響民意。同時，第一同二點，和理非心地太善良，當勇武真係做得岀後你地實屌，好啲嘅最多唔岀聲但心入面好不滿，怪責勇武影響運動形象。<br />\n<br />\n我真係想問，831後打死唔割，真係做到？<br />\n係嘅就俾啲信心勇武，投俾勇武睇。<br />\n<br />\n永不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n形象好緊要，唔好太盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385dfb1d253a693c1117cad33f919ebcbe5d5803","tid":1526644,"uid":263058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5170987b5b1d07491c25942c200634292890105","tid":1526644,"uid":132999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"唔割<br />\n<br />\n721 之後已經係"},{"pid":"012d85810b3dc9afb7de05892b385fb08e7b451b","tid":1526644,"uid":60398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:46:26.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s